data.description: BRAND NEW ROOF! Welcome to 303 Vaniman Ave, a charming home nestled in the heart of Winter Haven. This delightful single-family home boasts a perfect blend of classic and contemporary design, offering both comfort and style. As you approach the property, you’ll be greeted by lush landscaping and a fully fenced yard. Step inside, and you’ll discover a spacious and inviting living area with plenty of natural light flowing through large windows. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining or family gatherings. The kitchen features modern appliances, ample cabinet and counter space. This property includes three comfortable bedrooms, each offering a tranquil retreat for rest and relaxation. The primary bedroom boasts an ensuite half bathroom for added convenience, while the remaining bedrooms share a well-appointed full bathroom. Sliding glass doors lead to a private backyard oasis, complete with a screened-in lanai, covered outdoor cooking space and several producing fruit trees including mango and avocado! The backyard provides an ideal setting for outdoor relaxation and recreation. Additional features of this home include a two space carport, a laundry room, and proximity to the amenities and attractions that make Winter Haven a desirable place to live. Enjoy the convenience of being close to schools, parks, shopping, and dining, all within a short drive. Don’t miss the opportunity to make 303 Vaniman Ave your new home in Winter Haven, where you can experience the best of Florida living in a comfortable setting.
